            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%9D%A1%E8%A7%89%E6%97%B6%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E6%8A%96%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%AA%E7%B4%AF%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%9D%A1%E8%A7%89%E6%97%B6%E8%BA%AB%E4%BD%93%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E6%8A%96%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%AA%E7%B4%AF%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#睡觉时身体突然抖一下可能是太累了#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[困]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kun-0f87c3e1f8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[睡]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuijiao-4cb62c7d81.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】 你有没有过这样的经历？睡着没多久，身体突然抖了一下，同时可能还伴随着跌落或踏空的感觉？其实这是一种正常的生理现象，医学上叫作临睡肌抽跃症，是一种无意识的肌肉颤搐。睡觉时身体为什么会抖一下？什么情况下需要及时就医？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4919353569640509" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hfjh2ftyeaj21hc0u041q.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/X1Agwbknlx086IdFPOo801041200jPLg0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688505322&amp;ssig=VsH9NGkCq0&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/OYgb884Ylx086IdFqPmw010412009kS70E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688505322&amp;ssig=roabSe3Hau&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/6ZWtOd5elx086IdF5RrG010412005HWW0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1688505322&amp;ssig=3dzvvpwtox&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4919353569640509&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
